@EndNode

@Node "FaxOutStack" "GMS_Mailer.guide/MailerSettings/Fax/FaxOutStack"
@Next "FaxString"
@Prev "FaxOutCommand"
@Toc  "cfgFax"

Name:      FaxOutStack=<dimensione>

   Sets the stack size for <FaxOutCommand> command.


Example:   FaxOutStack=8000

@EndNode

@Node "FaxString" "GMS_Mailer.guide/MailerSettings/Fax/FaxString"
@Next ""
@Prev "FaxOutStack"
@Toc  "cfgFax"

