Future
******

   This is a small to do file of the features of the next version of
GMS_Mailer:

- Janus and  DietIfna file transfer protocols.
- FTS-1/Lotek handshake.
- Preferences editor.
- Triton and EGS System supports.
- OwnDevUnit.library supports.
- Nodelist e ptlist 5D processor.
- Docs in texinfo, tex and ps formats.

   And some secret features...

@EndNode
